{"tid":1376970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋就黎輸了 同佢死過","createTime":"2019-07-28T12:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T12:42:46.000Z","uid":277996,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10f598e163380517cbc839973e076533c1ef8f87","tid":1376970,"uid":277996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:41:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家仲唔明政府嘅處理手法？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好似雨傘嗰陣時咁 拖得就拖</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家唔博命幾時博？等到九月啲學生開學？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">狗嘅武器威力一日大過一日</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你哋仲等乜？等佢哋出真槍？出水炮車？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我真係唔想我哋之前所做嘅嘢白費</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔通我地真係由得兄弟俾人打？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">真係係時候還手</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你哋睇吓外國啲示威</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持以武制暴 係時候以傷換傷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">各位巴打絲打我行先了 有緣再見</span></span>"},{"pid":"4bef0b927815b689601088eebb112f8f2a62ce65","tid":1376970,"uid":277996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5d171d4511557aa34f4f8871618b6ca6efce51","tid":1376970,"uid":277996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4eba51f450b4aa685b2963a0086519c95897fb","tid":1376970,"uid":277996,"like":0